## API Routes

The application includes the following API endpoints:

- `GET /api/status` - Health check
- `POST /api/contact` - Contact form submission
- `GET /api/todos` - Get all todos (authenticated)
- `POST /api/todos` - Create a new todo (authenticated)
- `PUT /api/todos/:id` - Update a todo (authenticated)
- `DELETE /api/todos/:id` - Delete a todo (authenticated)

## Authentication

The app uses Better Auth for authentication with the following features:

- Email and password authentication
- Session management
- Protected routes
- Type-safe session handling

## Development

### Adding New Components

Components are built using Shadcn/ui. Add new components:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```

### Database Changes

When modifying database schemas:

1. Update schema files in `src/db/schema/`
2. Generate migrations: `npm run db:generate`
3. Apply migrations: `npm run db:migrate`

### API Development

API routes are built with Hono.js. Add new routes in `src/hono/routes/`.

